name: WHAT DO YOU MEAN?!
description:
Controls:
WASD or arrows to move.
Left click to PUNCH!!

You arrive to Professor Dogette's lab.
But wait, this isn't how it usually goes..?!

Theme interpretation: You cannot have any of the four elements.
If there's no fifth element, you make it!

Credits:

Crusenho - Mouse icon (Part of a set of icons)

ELV Games - Fantasy Dreamland tileset

Phyrnna - That one cool song at the end of the game. (URL-less)
Check her music, she rocked on the Epic Battle Fantasy series!

JSFXR - Generated some sounds.

The rest is completely by me, including the first two music tracks, any art that's not in the Fantasy Dreamland tileset, and all of the code! :D

Some of the assets already existed prior to the jam, so I decided to recycle them.
Art's mostly from the 30 days of pixel art challenge I've had.
Music's just original stuff, lying around.
